(2648, NULL, NULL, 'Yuri', NULL, 'Encontrei aqui! Reproduzo abaixo a mensagem original:<p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">Professor, apenas para confirmar, os módulos deve ser:&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Moedor - Gubi&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Inseção Manual - Antonio</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Concordanciador&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">- Clayton</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Metaplasmador&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Componentes Morfológicos&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Hiperlema&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Metalema&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Abreviatura - Yuri</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Obra - Yuri&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Morfológica/SemÃ¢ntica&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">-Geral&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px;">-Savenew - Antonio</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px;">-Fórum - Yuri</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">Como mexi mais recentemente com o Concordanciador e Obras, começarei por eles. A medida que eu for concluindo os 2, vou pegando outros ou então quem mais quiser pegar vai avisando no que está trabalhando, para evitar trabalho perdido. Caso falte algum, avise Mário.</span></p>', '2015-03-10 00:02:21', 2539, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 14, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, now(), now()),
