(2910, NULL, NULL, 'maeviaro', NULL, 'Também aconteceu o mesmo com esta obra:<p><br></p><p><p class="main" style="color: red; font-size: 20px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/consulta_obra.php#" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">"Ariano Suassuna - aventuras de um cavaleiro do sertão". In: Jornal do Brasil (20/09/1972) ed. 153</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">Autor:</p><p class="small" style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: red;">Obra inserida via moedor</p><p class="small" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">Concedente: Jornal do Brasil</p><p class="small" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;"><br></p><p class="small" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">Nem o nome do autor, nem a localização aparecem.</p><p class="small" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">Curiosamente, inseri o concedente agora e ele apareceu.</p></p>', '2015-03-25 01:28:52', 2901, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, now(), now()),
