(4012, 1, 2, 'maeviaro', 'ANTÔNIO - palavras compostas', 'Prazo: até 20-05-2015<p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Meus caros, tenho um problemão que na verdade é um probleminha e gostaria de resolvê-lo o quanto antes.</span><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Como sabem, a coleta de variantes tem regras e uma delas é que duas sequências de caracteres separadas por um espaço em branco no texto original convertem-se em duas variantes no moedor e no concordanciador.&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Isso porém gera problemas estranhÃ­ssimos para os linguistas e problemas quase insolúveis para os programadores.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Depois de muito pensar, acho que achei uma solução:</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Vejam o caso de "Mato Grosso" em busca Dicionário</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-size: medium; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><span class="main" style="color: red; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px;"><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Acepcao&amp;id=11301" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Mato Grosso</a>&nbsp;</span>(13/04/1769)</p><p class="descript" style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); line-height: normal; font-size: 13.6000003814697px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><span class="versalete" style="font-variant: small-caps;">Classificação morfológica:&nbsp;</span>Substantivo masculino</p><p class="descript" style=