(4038, 1, 2, 'maeviaro', 'ANTÔNIO - Numerais', '<p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Antônio, acho que me embananei tempos atrás. Ã‰ preciso novamente corrigir a &nbsp;classificação morfológica de novo! &nbsp;Desculpe.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Ao escolher a classe&nbsp;<i>Numeral,&nbsp;</i>abre-se a opção&nbsp;<i>Tipo.&nbsp;</i></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><i><br></i></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">O tipo Cardinal só tem gênero (masculino/ feminino/ Invariável).</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Por exemplo: dois/duas</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Faltou um gênero: Invariável</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Por exemplo: três</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">O tipo Ordinal tem gênero (masculino e feminino) e número (singular e plural).</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Por exemplo: primeiro/ primeira/primeiros/ primeiras</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">(nesse caso não há gênero Invariável nem número Invariável)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: helvetica, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(225, 225, 225, now(, now(), now()), now());">Atualmente está invertido!</p><p><br></p>', '2015-05-21 00:35:55', 0, '2015-05-23 00:21:26', 5, 1, '', 9, NULL, now(), now()),
