(4349, NULL, NULL, 'maeviaro', NULL, 'Não ficou bom.&nbsp;<p><br><p>Em "água" (id 11247) aparece</p><p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><span class="info versalete" style="font-variant: small-caps;">Flexões:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Flexao&amp;id=11556">água (13/04/1769)- (singular)</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Flexao&amp;id=11559">águas (13/04/1769)- (plural)</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><span class="info versalete" style="font-variant: small-caps;">Variantes:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Variante&amp;id=11730">agoa (13/04/1769)</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Variante&amp;id=11978">aguas (29/03/1849)</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Variante&amp;id=11733">agoas (13/04/1769)</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><br></p></p><p>aparentemente está correto, se clico em "água" esperaria que aparecesse apenas a variante "agoa", no entanto, aparece assim:</p><p><p class="title" style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); line-height: normal;"><br></p><p class="title" style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); line-height: normal;">Abonações:</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">agoa: " hé esta Caxueira mto perigóza pelas mtas Pedras, e Redomoinhos e ondas de&nbsp;<b>agoa</b>&nbsp;q forma; e isto em grande dist*ncia." (13/04/1769)</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">aguas: " O que unicamente preocupa a estes meus senhores é descobrir modo e maneira de fermentar e excitar as paixões dá multidão - para pôr em convulsão a sociedade; querem por este meio ver se pescam nas&nbsp;<b>aguas</b>&nbsp;turvas." (29/03/1849)</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.42857143;">se clico em "águas" deveria aparecer as variantes "aguas" e "agoas", no entanto aparece apenas a segunda:</span></p><p class="title" style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); line-height: normal;"><br></p><p class="title" style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); line-height: normal;">Abonações:</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">agoas: " No meyo deste Canal onde as&nbsp;<b>agoas</b>&nbsp;éraõ ja mais mansas fizemos alto, segurando-nos no módo possivel a esperar que passacem todas as outras Canoas aquelle perigo, e vendo a huma pr huã se se perdia, ou se sahia a salvamto; pois em esta Caxueira se tem perdido mtas Embarcaçoens, fazendas, e mtos homens afogados." (13/04/1769)</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.42857143;">Não entendo o que pode estar acontecendo</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.42857143;"><br></span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.42857143;">Não esqueça também que as flexões deveriam estar como eu disse acima (sem a data):</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="line-height: 1.42857143;"><br></span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><span class="info versalete" style="font-variant: small-caps;">Flexões:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Flexao&amp;id=11556">água (singular)</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/alpha/paginas/editar.php?nivel=Flexao&amp;id=11559">águas (plural)</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height