(4900, 1, 2, 'maeviaro', 'Erro na página', 'Inseri as obras da Renata e tudo deu certinho. Parabéns!&nbsp;<p><br></p><p>No entanto, quando eu estou na moagem e mudo o nome do pesquisador, tudo dá certo, por exemplo:</p><p><br></p><p>http://www.nehilp.org/cgi/alpha/novopesq?novo_usu=142&amp;sessao=393</p><p><h1 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; background-color: rgb(235, 235, 235, now(, now(), now()), now());"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif;">Trocado o pesquisador da sessão 393 para 142!</span></h1><h1 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; background-color: rgb(235, 235, 235, now(, now(), now()), now());"><p></p></h1><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; background-color: rgb(235, 235, 235, now(, now(), now()), now());"><a href="http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/paginas/moagens.php">Voltar</a></b></p><p><br></p><p>mas se clico em voltar acontece isso:</p><p><br></p><p>http://www.nehilp.org/~nehilp/paginas/moagens.php</p><p><br></p><p><h1 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: normal;">Not Found</h1><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">The requested URL /~nehilp/paginas/moagens.php was not found on this server.</p><hr style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, now(, now(), now()), now()); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><address style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0, n